text: Camel Toe is a comedy album by The Bob & Tom Show, which was first released in November 2003. It is a two-disc set which represents original material recorded during their syndicated, daily radio show and other studio numbers which had not been previously presented on air. ==Track listings== == References == Category:2003 albums Category:The Bob & Tom Show albums Category:2000s comedy albums
title: Camel Toe (album)
